<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٦٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا لَمْ تُحِطْ بِهِ خُبْرًا}</span> ... مَا يَخْفَى عَلَيْكِ عِلْمُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَرَقَهَا}</span> ... قَلَعَ لَوْحًا مِنْ أَلْوَاحِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِمْرًا}</span> ... أَمْرًا مُنْكَرًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا تُرْهِقْنِي}</span> ... لَا تُكَلِّفْنِي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَكِيَّةً}</span> ... طَاهِرَةً لَمْ تَبْلُغْ حَدَّ التَّكْلِيفِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُّكْرًا}</span> ... مُنْكَرًا عَظِيمًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَطْعَمَا أَهْلَهَا}</span> ... طَلَبَا طَعامًا عَلَى سَبِيلِ الضِّيَافَةِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُرِيدُ أَنْ يَنقَضَّ}</span> ... يُوشِكُ أَنْ يَسْقُطَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِتَاوِيلِ}</span> ... بِمَآلِ، وَعَاقِبَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرَاءَهُم}</span> ... أَمَامَهُمْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كُلَّ سَفِينَةٍ}</span> ... كُلَّ سَفِينَةٍ صَالِحَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٨٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُرْهِقَهُمَا}</span> ... يُكَلِّفَهُمَا، وَيُحَمِّلَهُمَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٨١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَكَاةً}</span> ... صَلَاحًا، وَطَهَارَةً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٨١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَقْرَبَ رُحْمًا}</span> ... بِرًّا بِهِمَا، وَرَحْمَةً عَلَيْهِمَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٨٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَبْلُغَا أَشُدَّهُمَا}</span> ... يَكْبَرَا، وَيَبْلُغَا قَوَّتَهُمَا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
